<plot>Richard (Michel Piccolo) is a medieval nobleman. After his first wife dies in an accident and is buried in the family vault, he remarries and has children by his second wife. A mad longing for his first wife Leonor (Liv Ullmann) comes over him, and he sells his soul to the devil for a chance to get her back. But when she returns, she is a murderous vampire.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?329474</url></doc>
